Trinity::

She woke up in the CR.  She felt funny all over and giggled a bit.  
THe regeration lined tickled her sides as they retracted. She hit the 
button to open the door and stepped out. She looked at her side and 
saw that it was perfectly healed up. She smiled and walked out to the 
others. "Hey all, did I miss much?" She looked over at Zeni, "Is he 
going to be ok?"
